        It is our policy to ensure that each person who adopts a pokémon is aware of the responsibilities of pet guardianship, and
        is capable of and willing to accept those responsibilities morally, physically and financially. Not every person who desires to
        adopt a pokémon should do so.
        By completing this questionnaire, you will aid us in determining if you and your family are indeed ready for pet guardianship,
        and if the pokémon of your interest would suit you and your lifestyle. Should you agree that adopting a pet is a commitment
        throughout the lifetime of your companion animal, please fill out this questionnaire.
    </p>
